description.narrative:
The objetives of the intervention are:
to combine resources, infrastructures, and strengths of multiple countries in order to facilitate innovative research projects to curb AMR with a One Health approach;
to support and increase the participation of researchers in low-income countries in sub-Saharan Africa and other sub-Saharan countries where Sweden has bilateral development cooperation in the global fight against AMR;
to build capacity and support the formation of a network of AMR researchers on the African continent.
